snippet.title: [MISTOVER] Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
MISTOVER: Explore the Mist to decide the fate of Mankind
''MIST-ical' RPG with expeditions for finding the key to survival. Choose your next step wisely and keep in mind that your every move will change the future.

Official site: https://www.playmistover.com/home       
Steam Store: https://store.steampowered.com/app/909510/MISTOVER/
Nintendo Switch eShop: To be Announced.
